Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是中央集散中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是邮差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将四处收集到的货物暂时集中在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后领取自己负责投递的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂 纱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作习惯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道该怎么做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…正在一点一点地学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有艾米前辈的指导 马上就能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是下午需要投递的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够三个人分工真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有分在同一个区了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 就来问我说像我这样的女孩会想要什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想要鞋子呢 因为很快就会磨破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说他把我往哪搁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 应该说他心思不够细腻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人就别管了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 有男朋友的人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 分完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样细分之后 配送起来也会比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的船我还没全部记住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近都是我之前所在的舰团的船 所以我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那边是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 过来一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人别靠近这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 麦塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉玛 不可以打扰别人工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你是技师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这里是怎么加工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合金的比率是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,促动器的扭矩有多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.69,ruby,NTP,0000,0310,0000,,actuator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢机械的话就来我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一段时间很缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说皮尼欧 你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 飞机头先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我现在想更多了解加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你们能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船就以将整个船体拉起来的方针来打捞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为接收了库盖尔舰团的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在必须增加船只的数量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那艘船相当大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞起来后放哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让库罗诺亚号的农场尽快结束收割的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那里应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可是大阵仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 久等了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 我都一身汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作后泡个澡真是爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你发现的沉船决定打捞上来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的秘密武器要得到久违的出场机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 等着瞧吧 保证你吓破胆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在库盖尔舰团里相当于是莉玛为我带路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 年纪轻轻的却很能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还「年纪轻轻」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不就只比你小一岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你们都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 今天雷德立大功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他刚才没跟我说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们又一起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔刚蒂亚上还真是有不少不错的设备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 我要海藻混合饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:11:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原大海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我休假中的大海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且休假要暂时结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近期会有一次大型打捞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止被打扰 由我们负责开道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的保镖工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有在认真工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在接受艾米的工作指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快递方面的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所乘坐的会飞的人形机器人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于战斗的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵重力在空中飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以理解语言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在任何时刻 都会凭借强大力量保护驾驶员的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的铠甲 Machine Caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和天神的使者一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 天神…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是Striker吗？库盖尔中校所乘坐的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我来自于库盖尔大人的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 可以告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校和Striker到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么 转移目标了？劈腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 莉玛的心情倒也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 如果得不到百分之百的关注 少女可是会不安的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 艾米她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她都悄悄去找Chamber商量了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…雷德有没有什么想要的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉所需要的食物和生活物资现在都得到了稳定的供给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指他收到了会觉得高兴的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让他露出笑脸的东西…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经判明同盟标准的娱乐程序对少尉没有任何效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不对啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能更了解雷德呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为…为什么你们会知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是建议啦 建议…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事用不着啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾米？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了 争风吃醋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人莞尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一个个都这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活充实是件好事 不过工作那边怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打捞虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也是时候觉得摆弄机械很有趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等等 皮尼欧 你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧常常会教我关于人形机器人构造方面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可怜他天天被甲壳屁股责骂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谁是甲壳屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想知道中校所率领的舰团为什么会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在库盖尔大人和使者大人开始引导人们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船加入了他们的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团上下将库盖尔大人奉为天神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而团结了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在利用鲸乌贼制造的叛乱结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽娜莉亚大人和艾蕾莉亚大人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都要为维持舰团献出自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连死也不过是其中的一种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了维持强大而舍弃弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强迫无法战斗的人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灌输为集体献身才是幸福的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是人类银河同盟的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为中校渴望那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人知道库盖尔大人到底是什么时候死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果中校活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果应该不会是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所认识的中校 曾经无数次拯救过我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没找到相关的资料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查Chamber的事很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为能从留下的操纵席上了解一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它所使用的技术还是远远超过了旧文明的水准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲留给妹妹丽娜莉亚的书籍已经全都在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 没帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些书里有很多加尔刚蒂亚上没有的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知这颗星球将会成为冰封的星球之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类分裂成两大阵营开始了斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同时也有一小群人试图探寻其他的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是那些人的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都放下了矜持 不顾一切地想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在斗争的同时启程奔向星河世界的人们应该也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 那些人抛弃了地球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是如此 我也更愿意相信他们是有过一番挣扎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了地球的人们后来的境遇如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有我一个人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 应该有些事是只有知情的我才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在寻找是否有能与鲸乌贼交流的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有能更加和平地 从容地共存的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这就像是我个人的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你必须抱有这种心情才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 我一直都在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟现在也还在和希迪亚斯进行着殊死的全面战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隐约认为这是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…你现在不是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前所在的宇宙在很远的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就没必要那样去想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经和你没有任何关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这全都是相关的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是人类的所为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们与鲸乌贼为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么当希迪亚斯来到地球的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法和同盟会是不同的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否会已经找到了其他的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去而必须舍弃无法替代的东西的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 不会发生那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你无论何时…就连那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那个暴风雨的日子 你也和Chamber一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉玛 你都听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是有意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 可以的话请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场暴风雨中 雷德和Chamber怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚被冲走的船又被冲回来撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经放下隔离壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险起见 还是要确认一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这个区域的最后一艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起重机开动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各连接部位无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样继续警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.67,0:23:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急联络！与阿尔特弥亚号之间的连接濒临脱落！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.86,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：阿尔特弥亚（Artemia） 俗称丰年虾、卤虫、海猴子等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告详情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助钢索全部绷断 连接器也损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一部还完好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 两舷的汽艇都无法使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:32.02,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,screw boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团长 阿尔特弥亚号上有500多位居民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络桥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还有一架完好 但不知道能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法修吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙不过来 迅速修理应该是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被害情况的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让无法控制的中型船漂流会让整个舰团也陷入危险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸沉阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特弥亚号…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将阿尔特弥亚号全员退舰作为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.55,0:24:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸沉阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.87,0:24:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧进行引导！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌张！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:24:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:24:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…纱雅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐还…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.68,0:25:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.21,0:25:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.25,0:25:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要炸沉的话我也一起死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.30,0:25:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 别撒娇了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我死都不会走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.35,0:25:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.93,0:25:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹在四处确认居民的撤离情况
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.78,0:25:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.67,0:25:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗莱斯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.13,0:25:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵转不动 死待在舰桥上也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.88,0:25:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这里是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.96,0:25:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 到中央船舱为止的居民已经都撤走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 舰桥也只剩下我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间确认剩余的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.96,0:25:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.37,0:25:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…你怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.56,0:25:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要弃船所以我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.94,0:26:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在确认船上还有没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.38,0:26:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙 还剩下哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.25,0:26:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船首舱和船尾舱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.05,0:26:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去船首舱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.94,0:26:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.12,0:26:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 要放弃阿尔特弥亚号是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.16,0:26:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 现在正在组织退舰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.86,0:26:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.30,0:26:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.22,0:26:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上离开这艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.39,0:26:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.45,0:26:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.80,0:26:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.90,0:26:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.28,0:26:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.24,0:26:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.38,0:26:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等自沉处理完成后 我们也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.09,0:26:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只能这么做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:26:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要弃船…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.06,0:27:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.99,0:27:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠一部连接器的话 这艘船可能会撞上舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.24,0:27:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在事态演变成这样之前把船炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.14,0:27:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是我们成长的家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.80,0:27:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大风暴我也从来都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.89,0:27:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过人生在世 无能为力的事总是难免
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.27,0:27:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.53,0:27:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨浪正在接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.02,0:27:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.13,0:27:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.12,0:27:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不太清楚 再说一遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.06,0:27:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.77,0:27:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.59,0:28:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.84,0:28:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.27,0:28:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测到船舶的过度倾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.28,0:28:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 纱雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.65,0:28:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.34,0:28:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.49,0:28:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.90,0:29:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经突破极限倾斜角度！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.35,0:29:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 最大功率！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 钢索呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.25,0:29:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在撑着 能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.81,0:29:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 拉起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.73,0:29:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.85,0:29:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.74,0:29:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.51,0:29:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收到紧急通信
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.30,0:30:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.93,0:30:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特弥亚号被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.02,0:30:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅和艾米还在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.52,0:30:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.63,0:30:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该船舶的运行控制已失效 推测已经无法掌舵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.38,0:30:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在漂流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.03,0:30:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.94,0:30:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.23,0:30:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又不能离开这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.27,0:30:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 要撑住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.81,0:30:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.40,0:30:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 破废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.38,0:30:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回里面去！穿上这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.54,0:30:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.62,0:30:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟 糟了 船正在往回飘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.91,0:31:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体开始恢复平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.78,0:31:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了 船体开始恢复直立了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.64,0:31:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾斜角度逐渐减小
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测正在转入安定状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.32,0:31:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.88,0:31:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.66,0:32:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁级别 下调
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.87,0:32:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来发生过这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.31,0:32:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时是因为有Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.77,0:32:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算现在发生了同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也肯定不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.70,0:32:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为总是为自己所能做到的事竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.63,0:32:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.47,0:33:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 开始下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.74,0:33:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝罗兹 捕捞框正常下降
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.70,0:33:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 大家都听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.08,0:33:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要让一艘船从墓场中复生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宝贝中的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.05,0:33:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好把它捞上来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.02,0:33:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.00,0:33:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认周边的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.24,0:34:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 有你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.11,0:34:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.93,0:34:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你不用接着去送货吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.77,0:34:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的工作到此就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.29,0:34:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心雷德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.62,0:34:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.33,0:34:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 就这样保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.23,0:34:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 放出固定锚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你们几个准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.50,0:34:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一班 将引导钢索连接到船体上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.30,0:35:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二班 将主钢索从船底绕过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.12,0:35:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认连接情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.05,0:35:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认完毕！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.69,0:35:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入最后工序了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.98,0:35:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.38,0:35:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.45,0:35:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.49,0:35:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢索好像被什么给勾住了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.89,0:35:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要崩塌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.17,0:35:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧点 赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.93,0:36:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 有我撑着！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.37,0:36:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.91,0:36:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.88,0:36:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德还在下面！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.10,0:36:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.87,0:36:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断钢索的连接！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.54,0:36:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.87,0:36:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.53,0:37:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧气存量！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.90,0:37:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.49,0:37:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用氧气罐打开
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.17,0:37:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二氧化碳吸收剂紧急投入
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.82,0:37:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电池存量已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.82,0:37:33.23,ruby,NTP,0000,0230,0000,,battery
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.41,0:37:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制器正常
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.41,0:37:35.24,ruby,NTP,0000,0110,0000,,Manipulator
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.56,0:37:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认通信状态
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.51,0:37:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.33,0:37:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说通信缆线…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.68,0:37:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁来回句话！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.29,0:37:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.30,0:37:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面到底发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.10,0:38:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.51,0:38:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有瓦斯涌出来 周边崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.00,0:38:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德那小子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.23,0:38:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算还活着 备用氧气也该用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.43,0:38:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那就快点潜回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.35,0:38:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在接近那里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.92,0:38:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救助队也会被卷入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.38,0:38:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.81,0:38:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.38,0:38:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想想办法吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.96,0:38:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝罗兹…！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.57,0:38:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝罗兹！我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.15,0:38:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.79,0:39:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Machine Caliber K6821驾驶员 雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.35,0:39:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.71,0:39:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测由于希迪亚斯的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.35,0:39:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致整个机库处于漂流状态
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.63,0:39:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧给我恢复通信 你这废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.94,0:39:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议关闭电波发射机能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.67,0:39:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到多数希迪亚斯的生体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.96,0:39:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机有被探知的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.24,0:39:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.09,0:39:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能等着被它们吞噬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快发出求救信号！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.72,0:39:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能相信你这种机器的判断！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.91,0:39:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.29,0:39:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有判断都由专属驾驶员雷德少尉进行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.56,0:39:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵官能力的充分发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.73,0:39:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可使本机导出打开局面的最佳方法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.85,0:40:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你的威力取决于我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.13,0:40:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 期待贵官做出明智的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.59,0:40:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.98,0:40:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.62,0:40:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是你还是我 都一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.73,0:40:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.49,0:40:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是驾驶员支援启发连接系统
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让贵官获得更多的成果便是我的存在意义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.64,0:40:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.93,0:40:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 他让我要相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.42,0:40:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且他说他相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.54,0:40:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西也撑不了太久
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.07,0:40:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想 快想想！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.89,0:41:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多来点 把在这的家伙都拉过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.01,0:41:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储气瓶不够 能搬多少来就搬多少来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.01,0:41:50.49,ruby,NTP,0000,0540,0000,,Bombe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.50,0:41:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得这样才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.78,0:42:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集各位船主
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.55,0:42:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他们请求人力和物资协助
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 安排医疗队
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.70,0:42:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.26,0:42:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.67,0:42:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.72,0:42:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.31,0:42:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.35,0:42:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.27,0:42:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.72,0:42:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也应该能帮上什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.30,0:42:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.64,0:42:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该做的是另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.81,0:42:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.88,0:42:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用笑脸去迎接这些不要命的傻瓜们和雷德的归来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.38,0:42:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会平安带他回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.18,0:42:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.22,0:43:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.79,0:43:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.18,0:43:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.23,0:43:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉凯奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.71,0:43:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们慢吞吞的搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.75,0:43:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.48,0:44:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有我在附近了还在这种地方搞出死人来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.75,0:44:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是存心想让我睡不好觉么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.09,0:44:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉凯奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.04,0:44:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪块地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.82,0:44:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这缝隙里面
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.42,0:44:18.33,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.42,0:44:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.79,0:44:20.34,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Storonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.79,0:44:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.34,0:44:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.62,0:44:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好拉凯奇 就这么撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.42,0:44:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.47,0:44:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.87,0:44:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.47,0:45:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浮筒用的压缩空气释放到驾驶舱里了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.51,0:45:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.34,0:45:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.43,0:45:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会互相配合 同时把这里撑开
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在这个瞬间把四肢和浮筒从躯干部分离
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.73,0:45:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.55,0:45:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.43,0:45:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒数3下就开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.55,0:45:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.65,0:45:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.86,0:45:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.11,0:45:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.87,0:45:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.58,0:45:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.04,0:46:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体从里面出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.14,0:46:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德平安无事！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.88,0:46:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.26,0:46:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.69,0:46:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.31,0:46:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.00,0:46:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.71,0:46:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.36,0:47:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.61,0:47:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.18,0:47:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.06,0:49:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 进入下一个阶段
Comment: 0,0:49:20.70,0:49:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解【这句其实我听不懂…………我觉得应该是外星语吧Orz
