Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.41,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}波がざわめくだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:22.69,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何気ない幸せが溢れ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.37,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}はじまりの勇気 見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:34.90,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}回るよ 回るよ 世界は回るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.92,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心の羽根広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:42.75,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕らは今日を生きて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:47.84,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}たとえどんな風が吹いても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.02,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何度でも自由を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:57.00,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}羽ばたいて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.36,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}悲しみも乗り越えた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:06.38,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}光があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:50.61,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将聚散离合深埋心间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:57.49,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前进的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:04.63,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}记忆总以柔和的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:09.17,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}对我们报以微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}天空的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.41,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}与涛声一同作响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:22.69,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.37,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}让我们找到最初的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:34.90,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}日出日落 冬去春来 世界不断变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.92,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们张开心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:42.75,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度过一天又一天的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:47.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论面对怎样的风向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.02,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终朝着自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:57.00,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为那悲伤的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:06.38,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在着绽放的光芒
